T02TD2366E:8b-1: rang bzhin bdag med ma de ni //
T02TD2366E:8b-2: bdag gi go rims byed pa yin //
T02TD2366E:8b-3: chags pa med pa de yis ni //
T02TD2366E:8b-4: nyon mongs zhi bar byed pa yin //
T02TD2366E:8b-5: skye dang 'chi ba srid pa yin //
T02TD2366E:8b-6: 'khrul pa rnams ni spong ba yin //
T02TD2366E:8b-7: bde ba chen po ster byed pa'i //
T02TD2366E:8b-8: len gyi 'khrul pa ma yin no //
T02TD2366E:8b-9: des na kha dog dbyibs med de //
T02TD2366E:8b-10: tshad kyang yod pa ma mthong ngo //
T02TD2366E:8b-11: 'dod pa med pa de yis ni //
T02TD2366E:8b-12: nga rgyal skye ba mi 'dod do //
T02TD2366E:8b-13: gang tshe bdag med ma de ni //
T02TD2366E:8b-14: bdag gi snying la zhugs pa na //
T02TD2366E:8b-15: bdag dang gzhan rnams ma lus pa'i //
T02TD2366E:8b-16: dbye ba yod par ma mthong ngo //
T02TD2366E:8b-18: gar yang gnas pa ma yin te //
T02TD2366E:8b-19: nam mkha' yi ni ngo bo ltar //
T02TD2366E:8b-20: yongs su gsal bar snang ba yin //
T02TD2366E:8b-21: thub pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pa //
T02TD2366E:8b-22: ma lus pa dang ral pa ni //
T02TD2366E:8b-23: de ni me li bdag med mar //
T02TD2366E:8b-24: de ltar bdag med smra ba yin //
T02TD2366E:8b-25: n'a ro pandi ta'i glu rdzogs so//
